<p>We are inviting you to join us on the Auburn University campus to develop and conduat a biology research project in the lab of <a href="https://www.auburn.edu/cosam/departments/biology/biology-faculty/wolak/index.htm">Dr. Matthew Wolak</a>. Come, be part of the CASE REU and the Wolak Research Group <strong>BEETLES</strong> (<strong>B</strong>eetle <strong>E</strong>volution <strong>E</strong>quips <strong>T</strong>eachers and <strong>L</strong>earners through <strong>E</strong>ngaging in <strong>S</strong>cience) program!</p>

<h2 id="how-to-apply">How to apply</h2>

<h3 id="tentative-dates-may-13---july-19-2024">Tentative Dates May 13 - July 19, 2024</h3>

<p>To apply, please see the <a href="https://www.auburn.edu/cosam/departments/diversity/reu.htm">CASE REU website</a> for information and to submit your application.</p>

